parcel.description:
ONE / OFF invites you into Zach Murrys first solo exhibition, COSMOZACH:
Iterative Fantasy. Housed within our Black Arts District, Iterative Fantasy combines
COSMOZACHS influences of science fantasy and his commitment to the iterative
process. Of the exhibition he says, each one of these pieces is a strenuous,
conscious effort to improve at my craft, grow my technical ability, dive further
into my own version of science fantasy and how I can achieve certain results and
aesthetics, using 3D & 2D digital techniques. As a digital artist, I really am a work
in progress and my work is a visual embodiment of this truth. As you explore
the gallery, COSMOZACHs narration of each piece brings you deeper into his
world. COSMOZACHs approach to creating fantasy dreamscapes combines his
limitless imagination and curiosity with an unparalleled work ethic that allows
for continuous improvement in both his style and technique.
parcel.name: Zach Murray Iterative Fantasy Exhibition
